options.text: I'd like to trade in my tickets, please.
I have a question about my Achievement Diary.

0ae4bf0d-f6e4-4273-8cbc-49856d0d9937.title: Pirate Jackie the Fruit
0ae4bf0d-f6e4-4273-8cbc-49856d0d9937.text: Welcome to the Brimhaven Agility Arena!

dcd24255-355a-4c72-aff9-1f84ca0933bd.title: Pirate Jackie the Fruit
dcd24255-355a-4c72-aff9-1f84ca0933bd.text:
If ye want to know more talk to Cap'n Izzy, he found
it!

16c353e5-30bf-4a1f-ab53-9e63a39d48b4.title: Pirate Jackie the Fruit
16c353e5-30bf-4a1f-ab53-9e63a39d48b4.text:
I be the Jack o' Tickets. I exchange the tickets ye
collect in the Agility Arena for more stuff. Ye can
obtain more agility experience or some items ye won't
find anywhere else!

cdcb95ee-da22-476e-b193-b98cea84804a.title: <player>
cdcb95ee-da22-476e-b193-b98cea84804a.text: I'd like to trade in my tickets, please.

df900570-09a7-4446-bee0-e0cf11aacf69.title: Pirate Jackie the Fruit
df900570-09a7-4446-bee0-e0cf11aacf69.text: Aye, ye be on the right tack.

f75babab-99ea-4097-821e-5c3cdd1f7c39.title: <player>
f75babab-99ea-4097-821e-5c3cdd1f7c39.text: I have a question about my Achievement Diary.

options.text: What potions do these new herbs make?

dc8ed70b-e2c4-4c1f-b83a-0be9bf92ab8c.title: <player>
dc8ed70b-e2c4-4c1f-b83a-0be9bf92ab8c.text: What potions do these new herbs make?

d314c3cc-e226-4366-a509-aa39d3cf7587.title: Pirate Jackie the Fruit
d314c3cc-e226-4366-a509-aa39d3cf7587.text:
I be no herbalist but I were given the recipes to go
with these herbs...

13dff849-54df-42d6-be9d-792ef4200608.title: Pirate Jackie the Fruit
13dff849-54df-42d6-be9d-792ef4200608.text:
Snapdragon + red spiders' eggs
= Super restore potion.

461f4bae-b765-40f6-9b6b-40500a6a8015.title: Pirate Jackie the Fruit
461f4bae-b765-40f6-9b6b-40500a6a8015.text:
Arrr, it be a diary that tracks yer achievements on
Karamja. Once ye've explored enough, I give ye some
enchanted gloves, an' the people of Karamja reward ye
for yer hard work.

fe597898-8b9b-441c-aca4-844b8c410405.title: Postpone
fe597898-8b9b-441c-aca4-844b8c410405.text:
Missing trading in tickets
Awaiting brimhaven agility arena

748d94f9-809e-4b12-8e9e-6f9212238ed0.title: Pirate Jackie the Fruit
748d94f9-809e-4b12-8e9e-6f9212238ed0.text: Arrr, that depends what tier ye wants to know about.

d01aa3c5-d90b-4d1f-9956-20ec8bf5b3ed.title: Pirate Jackie the Fruit
d01aa3c5-d90b-4d1f-9956-20ec8bf5b3ed.text:
Ye gets a pair of special Karamja gloves. The seafarin'
folk who sail to Port Sarim and Ardougne will take ye
on board half price if ye be wearin' them.

d827669f-85ab-4eda-ad29-32f9c1c71891.title: Pirate Jackie the Fruit
d827669f-85ab-4eda-ad29-32f9c1c71891.text:
Arrr, I upgrade the Karamja gloves so ye gets a little
extra benefit in our Agility Arena with 'em on. Ye can
use the stepping stone in Shilo Village, an ye still gets
the easy rewards too.

232169ff-c97f-41d7-b1b0-0084707c1569.title: Pirate Jackie the Fruit
232169ff-c97f-41d7-b1b0-0084707c1569.text:
Arrr, I upgrade the Karamja gloves so they can take
ye to a special mine under Shilo Village. Ye still gets
the easy and medium rewards too.

f73f7f3f-d8be-4b78-9bb1-14f48b5304ae.title: Pirate Jackie the Fruit
f73f7f3f-d8be-4b78-9bb1-14f48b5304ae.text:
Arrr, ye can get double TokKul from the Fight Cave,
Inferno an' TzHaar-Ket-Rak's Challenges, an' have a
chance for double tickets in our Agility Arena 'ere.

a10fe561-49d9-47f9-883e-1677ed031161.title: Pirate Jackie the Fruit
a10fe561-49d9-47f9-883e-1677ed031161.text:
Ye can resurrect in the Fight Cave once per day, an'
use a lot of short-cuts around the island, an' even enter
some places fer free.

e0d1a0f1-1a45-4dc0-932b-057e7e74391b.title: Pirate Jackie the Fruit
e0d1a0f1-1a45-4dc0-932b-057e7e74391b.text:
I can make the metal dragons under Brimhaven give
ye bars as banknotes too, if ye likes. Ye still gets the
easy, medium an' hard rewards too.
